{"parentUuid":"b0f12979-0f32-4594-bdf8-091f23c3a0ce","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01FQa4wPpW2v7i9J4b5dbj5f","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The directory is empty — no `.framework/plan.md` and no argument provided pointing to a plan file.\n\nLaunch needs a plan to build from. Where's the plan you want to use? Options:\n- Pass a path: `/trellis-launch /path/to/plan.md`\n- Create `.framework/plan.md` first, then re-run\n- Describe what you want to build and I'll help draft a plan before launching"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":274,"cache_read_input_tokens":25772,"output_tokens":194,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":274,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":194,"cache_read_input_tokens":25772,"cache_creation_input_tokens":274,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":274},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaDWmcDjY413iTXEvrRa8","type":"assistant","uuid":"8b40ca7f-232b-484a-a698-88ccfd160ceb","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:20:41.524Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"type":"file-history-snapshot","messageId":"b0d32f1d-6969-403d-ac4b-1dea874f1ac2","snapshot":{"messageId":"b0d32f1d-6969-403d-ac4b-1dea874f1ac2","trackedFileBackups":{},"timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:20:51.835Z"},"isSnapshotUpdate":false}
{"parentUuid":"8b40ca7f-232b-484a-a698-88ccfd160ceb","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"0d73fe9a-5a32-4c46-a3bd-9c6801d585a2","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"I want to build a claude code plugin. The purpose of this is to educate the user about their vibe\n  coding.\n\n  Problem: Vibe coders have no clue what is happening under the hood of the project they are building.\n  For small projects that is fine. But for bigger projects having no knowledge or idea or ability to\n  explain what is happening under the hood is a recipe for disaster and proves the user is naive.\n\n  Solution: This plugin will help the user understand what is happening and explains concepts,\n  algorithms, tech stach, methodologies used and other critical aspects of the project. The plugin\n  launches a html page that teaches and educates the user."},"uuid":"b0d32f1d-6969-403d-ac4b-1dea874f1ac2","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:20:51.835Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"b0d32f1d-6969-403d-ac4b-1dea874f1ac2","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01QCJh16UJSARhCpdd7vrat3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":397,"cache_read_input_tokens":26046,"output_tokens":1354,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":397,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":1354,"cache_read_input_tokens":26046,"cache_creation_input_tokens":397,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":397},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaDWndsynD7jQHhNEA4VV","type":"assistant","uuid":"60af74ad-29ef-428c-9667-fc79fc18574e","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:21:07.190Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"60af74ad-29ef-428c-9667-fc79fc18574e","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01QCJh16UJSARhCpdd7vrat3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Before I draft the plan, I need a few scoping decisions — this shapes the whole build:\n\n**1. Plugin shape.** Claude Code plugins can expose commands, skills, agents, hooks, or MCP servers. I'd recommend a **slash command** (e.g. `/under-the-hood`) that analyzes the project and opens an HTML page. Simple, explicit, user-triggered. Agree, or do you want it to trigger automatically (e.g. after a session)?\n\n**2. Scope of analysis.** For v1, I'd recommend static analysis of the current project: package manifests, directory structure, key config files, plus a Claude-written narrative. Deeper (runtime tracing, git history, dependency graphs) adds a lot of complexity. OK to start shallow?\n\n**3. HTML style.** Single self-contained HTML file (inline CSS/JS, no build step) that opens in the browser? Or a richer site with diagrams (Mermaid) and interactive elements?\n\n**4. Stack assumption.** Any stack, or optimize for one (JS/Python/Flutter)? General-purpose is harder to do well.\n\n**5. Teaching depth.** Glossary + stack overview + architecture walkthrough? Or also include \"why this pattern was chosen\" / \"common pitfalls\"?\n\nAnswer these and I'll write `.framework/plan.md`, then we launch."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":397,"cache_read_input_tokens":26046,"output_tokens":1354,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":397,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":1354,"cache_read_input_tokens":26046,"cache_creation_input_tokens":397,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":397},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaDWndsynD7jQHhNEA4VV","type":"assistant","uuid":"01c15680-6342-45d5-ab0f-9f080cc35686","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:21:14.088Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
