{"parentUuid":"0b3057f0-5e69-4d80-b9bb-0adb79cf9239","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_016an5Yyy2gTGQ8bivrBKFM6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pausing before I write the plan — honest flag.\n\nTrellis is built for multi-screen apps with data/UI/logic/theme layers (Flutter-style). This project is a Claude Code plugin — really just:\n- 1 slash command (markdown)\n- 1 HTML template (self-contained)\n- 1 launcher script\n- 1 manifest JSON\n- 1 README\n\nForcing it through 6 phases (decompose → contracts → skeleton → parallel build → assembly → polish) will add ceremony without value. The \"components\" won't cleanly map to data/UI/logic layers. Parallel agent build is overkill for ~5 files.\n\n**Two paths:**\n\n1. **Skip Trellis.** I build the plugin directly — manifest, command, template, script, README. Fast, honest fit for the shape of the work. ~30 min of my time, no pipeline overhead.\n\n2. **Force Trellis.** I adapt the plan to fit the 4-layer template (data = analysis-schema, ui = html-template, logic = slash-command + launcher, theme = styling). You get state tracking + phase gates + an app-map at the end.\n\nMy recommendation: **path 1**. Trellis earns its complexity on 20+ component projects; this one doesn't need it.\n\nWhich do you want?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":653,"cache_read_input_tokens":32783,"output_tokens":812,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":653,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":812,"cache_read_input_tokens":32783,"cache_creation_input_tokens":653,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":653},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaE1oHbFG8xfTWpAYpxbJ","type