ation/json\"` script element (immune to HTML parser). The launcher must verify the JSON is valid before injecting.\n- `__WAID_PROJECT_NAME__` must be HTML-entity-escaped by the launcher before substitution (replace `&`, `<`, `>`, `\"`, `'`).\n- `__WAID_TEMPLATE_CSS__` and `__WAID_TEMPLATE_JS__` must NOT contain the literal string `</style>` or `</script>` respectively (they won't; CSS and JS don't naturally contain those). If they do the launcher must escape them.\nThe sentinels are designed to be collision-resistant: no valid JSON value, CSS rule, or JavaScript expression can contain the literal string `__WAID_ANALYSIS_JSON__` etc., so a single-pass `str.replace()` is safe.\n| `__WAID_ANALYSIS_JSON__` | Inside `<script id=\"waid-data\" type=\"application/json\">__WAID_ANALYSIS_JSON__</script>` in `<head>` | Valid JSON string conforming to AnalysisSchema (no surrounding quotes; raw JSON object) | If empty/missing: `window.WAID.init` receives `null`; page renders error banner `#waid-error` and hides all section cards |\n| `__WAID_ANALYSIS_JSON__` | Raw contents of `<analysis.json>` (trailing newline stripped) | `$ANALYSIS_JSON` file |\n| `__WAID_GENERATED_AT__` | ISO 8601 UTC timestamp: `YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ` | `date -u` at script runtime |\n| `__WAID_GENERATED_AT__` | `<meta name=\"waid:generated-at\" content=\"__WAID_GENERATED_AT__\">` in `<head>` | ISO-8601 datetime string (e.g. `2026-05-02T14:30:00Z`) — same as `meta.generated_at` in the JSON | If missing: meta tag has empty content; no visible effect |\n| `__WAID_PROJECT_NAME__` | `<title>__WAID_PROJECT_NAME__ — Under the Hood</title>` and `<h1 id=\"waid-title\">` inside `#waid-header` | Plain text project name (HTML-escaped by launcher before substitution) | If missing: title reads \"— Under the Hood\"; h1 is empty |\n| `__WAID_SCHEMA_VERSION__` | `<meta name=\"waid:schema-version\" content=\"__WAID_SCHEMA_VERSION__\">` in `<head>` | Semver string (e.g. `1.0.0`) | If missing: meta tag has empty content |\n| `__