t backgrounds |\n30\t| `--waid-color-accent-muted` | `#7da0f8` | `#3b5db8` | Hover states for accent elements |\n31\t| `--waid-color-code-bg` | `#1e2330` | `#101318` | Fenced code block background |\n32\t| `--waid-color-code-border` | `#2d3348` | `#1e2330` | Code block border |\n33\t| `--waid-color-severity-low` | `#1e7a4f` | `#34c47a` | Pitfall — low severity text/icon |\n34\t| `--waid-color-severity-low-bg` | `#edfaf3` | `#0d2a1c` | Pitfall — low severity card bg |\n35\t| `--waid-color-severity-low-border` | `#a3dfc0` | `#1a4a32` | Pitfall — low severity border |\n36\t| `--waid-color-severity-medium` | `#92620a` | `#f0b94a` | Pitfall — medium severity text/icon |\n37\t| `--waid-color-severity-medium-bg` | `#fef9ec` | `#2a1e08` | Pitfall — medium severity card bg |\n38\t| `--waid-color-severity-medium-border` | `#f5d48a` | `#4a3410` | Pitfall — medium severity border |\n39\t| `--waid-color-severity-high` | `#b02020` | `#f27272` | Pitfall — high severity text/icon |\n40\t| `--waid-color-severity-high-bg` | `#fff0f0` | `#2a0e0e` | Pitfall — high severity card bg |\n41\t| `--waid-color-severity-high-border` | `#f5baba` | `#4a1818` | Pitfall — high severity border |\n42\t| `--waid-color-chip-bg` | `#eceef2` | `#1c2029` | Tech-stack chip background |\n43\t| `--waid-color-chip-text` | `#2e3442` | `#b0b8cc` | Tech-stack chip text |\n44\t| `--waid-color-chip-border` | `#dde1e7` | `#2a2f3a` | Tech-stack chip border |\n45\t| `--waid-color-toggle-bg` | `#dde1e7` | `#2a2f3a` | Toggle track background |\n46\t| `--waid-color-toggle-thumb` | `#ffffff` | `#e8eaf0` | Toggle thumb |\n47\t| `--waid-color-focus-ring` | `#3b72f2` | `#5d8fff` | Keyboard focus outline |\n48\t| `--waid-color-quiz-correct` | `#1e7a4f` | `#34c47a` | Quiz correct-answer highlight |\n49\t| `--waid-color-quiz-incorrect` | `#b02020` | `#f27272` | Quiz incorrect-answer highlight |\n50\t\n51\t**Total color tokens: 32**\n52\t\n53\t---\n54\t\n55\t## Typography Tokens\n56\t\n57\tNo CDN or `@import`. All stacks use system fonts with one fallback tier.\n58\t\n59\t**Font families**\n60\t\n61\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n62\t|---|---|---|\n63\t| `--waid-font-sans` | `\"Inter\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, sans-serif` | Body copy, headings, UI labels |\n64\t| `--waid-font-mono` | `\"JetBrains Mono\", \"Fira Code\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Courier New\", monospace` | Code blocks, inline code |\n65\t\n66\t**Type scale** — 1.2 (minor third) ratio, base 16 px\n67\t\n68\t| Token | Size | rem | Usage |\n69\t|---|---|---|---|\n70\t| `--waid-fs-xs` | 11 px | `0.6875rem` | Tertiary labels, chip text |\n71\t| `--waid-fs-sm` | 13 px | `0.8125rem` | Secondary labels, metadata, TOC items |\n72\t| `--waid-fs-base` | 16 px | `1rem` | Body copy |\n73\t| `--waid-fs-md` | 19 px | `1.1875rem` | Sub-section headings (h3) |\n74\t| `--waid-fs-lg` | 23 px | `1.4375rem` | Section headings (h2) |\n75\t| `--waid-fs-xl` | 28 px | `1.75rem` | Page-level headings (h1-equivalent) |\n76\t| `--waid-fs-2xl` | 33 px | `2.0625rem` | Report title |\n77\t| `--waid-fs-3xl` | 40 px | `2.5rem` | Hero / cover display (reserved) |\n78\t\n79\t**Font weights**\n80\t\n81\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n82\t|---|---|---|\n83\t| `--waid-fw-regular` | `400` | Body copy |\n84\t| `--waid-fw-medium` | `500` | Labels, TOC items, chip text |\n85\t| `--waid-fw-semibold` | `600` | Sub-headings, card titles |\n86\t| `--waid-fw-bold` | `700` | Section headings, report title |\n87\t\n88\t**Line heights**\n89\t\n90\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n91\t|---|---|---|\n92\t| `--waid-lh-tight` | `1.25` | Headings, chips, single-line UI |\n93\t| `--waid-lh-snug` | `1.4` | Labels, TOC items |\n94\t| `--waid-lh-body` | `1.6` | Body copy (exceeds WCAG minimum 1.5) |\n95\t| `--waid-lh-code` | `1.55` | Code blocks |\n96\t\n97\t**Letter spacing**\n98\t\n99\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n100\t|---|---|---|\n101\t| `--waid-ls-tight` | `-0.01em` | Large headings |\n102\t| `--waid-ls-normal` | `0em` | Body, code |\n103\t| `--waid-ls-wide` | `0.04em` | Uppercase labels, chip text |\n104\t\n105\t**Total typography tokens: 23** (2 family + 8 scale + 4 weight + 4 line-height + 3 letter-spacing + family enumeration in component styles)\n106\t\n107\t---\n108\t\n109\t## Spacing Tokens\n110\t\n111\t4 px base grid.\n112\t\n113\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n114\t|---|---|---|\n115\t| `--waid-space-1` | `4px` | Tight padding inside chips, icon gaps |\n116\t| `--waid-space-2` | `8px` | Inline padding, small gaps |\n117\t| `--waid-space-3` | `12px` | Input / button vertical padding |\n118\t| `--waid-space-4` | `16px` | Card inner padding (mobile), list item gap |\n119\t| `--waid-space-6` | `24px` | Card inner padding (desktop), section gap |\n120\t| `--waid-space-8` | `32px` | Between major sections |"}]},"uuid":"8d337690-c570-47eb-bca4-dcf845201a5b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T05:55:07.628Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing/.framework/contracts/theme/DesignTokens.contract.md","content":"# DesignTokens Contract\n\nLayer: theme\n\n## Responsibility\n\nDefine all CSS custom properties (color, typography, spacing, radii, shadows, motion) consumed by every UI component in the `waid` HTML report, ensuring a calm, content-first appearance that remains legible in both light and dark modes.\n\n---\n\n## Color Tokens\n\nAll values live on `:root` (light defaults) and are overridden under `[data-theme=\"dark\"]`. The `auto` variant is handled in CSS via `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` inside a `[data-theme=\"auto\"]` block.\n\n| Token | Light Value | Dark Value | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `--waid-color-bg-base` | `#fefefe` | `#0e1014` | Page background |\n| `--waid-color-bg-surface` | `#f5f6f8` | `#14171d` | Cards, sidebar, code-block bg |\n| `--waid-color-bg-sunken` | `#eceef2` | `#0b0d10` | Inset areas, quiz choice bg |\n| `--waid-color-bg-overlay` | `#ffffff` | `#1c2029` | Tooltips, dropdowns |\n| `--waid-color-border` | `#dde1e7` | `#2a2f3a` | Card borders, dividers |\n| `--waid-color-border-subtle` | `#eceef2` | `#1e2229` | Subtle separators |\n| `--waid-color-text-primary` | `#111318` | `#e8eaf0` | Body copy, headings |\n| `--waid-color-text-secondary` | `#4a5260` | `#8b93a4` | Captions, metadata, labels |\n| `--waid-color-text-tertiary` | `#7a8499` | `#5c6475` | Placeholder, disabled |\n| `--waid-color-text-inverse` | `#ffffff` | `#111318` | Text on filled accent bg |\n| `--waid-color-text-code` | `#1a2a44` | `#c9d8f0` | Inline code text |\n| `--waid-color-accent` | `#3b72f2` | `#5d8fff` | Links, active TOC, focus rings |\n| `--waid-color-accent-subtle` | `#eef2fe` | `#1a2545` | Accent tint backgrounds |\n| `--waid-color-accent-muted` | `#7da0f8` | `#3b5db8` | Hover states for accent elements |\n| `--waid-color-code-bg` | `#1e2330` | `#101318` | Fenced code block background |\n| `--waid-color-code-border` | `#2d3348` | `#1e2330` | Code block border |\n| `--waid-color-severity-low` | `#1e7a4f` | `#34c47a` | Pitfall — low severity text/icon |\n| `--waid-color-severity-low-bg` | `#edfaf3` | `#0d2a1c` | Pitfall — low severity card bg |\n| `--waid-color-severity-low-border` | `#a3dfc0` | `#1a4a32` | Pitfall — low severity border |\n| `--waid-color-severity-medium` | `#92620a` | `#f0b94a` | Pitfall — medium severity text/icon |\n| `--waid-color-severity-medium-bg` | `#fef9ec` | `#2a1e08` | Pitfall — medium severity card bg |\n| `--waid-color-severity-medium-border` | `#f5d48a` | `#4a3410` | Pitfall — medium severity border |\n| `--waid-color-severity-high` | `#b02020` | `#f27272` | Pitfall — high severity text/icon |\n| `--waid-color-severity-high-bg` | `#fff0f0` | `#2a0e0e` | Pitfall — high severity card bg |\n| `--waid-color-severity-high-border` | `#f5baba` | `#4a1818` | Pitfall — high severity border |\n| `--waid-color-chip-bg` | `#eceef2` | `#1c2029` | Tech-stack chip background |\n| `--waid-color-chip-text` | `#2e3442` | `#b0b8cc` | Tech-stack chip text |\n| `--waid-color-chip-border` | `#dde1e7` | `#2a2f3a` | Tec