{"parentUuid":"32c0a188-8ff9-42d2-8d29-6adb3103ddf0","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01DxbV1t6LqqqLuWAZSHy5qm","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Phase 2 Contracts complete — your review gate.**\n\n7 contract files written:\n\n```\n.framework/contracts/\n├── data/\n│   ├── AnalysisSchema.contract.md       (full JSON Schema for analysis output)\n│   └── StackDetectionRules.contract.md  (11 stacks: node, py, rust, go, flutter, java, ruby, php, .net, swift, unknown)\n├── ui/\n│   ├── HtmlTemplate.contract.md         (4 placeholders, DOM contract, sections)\n│   └── InteractiveJS.contract.md        (window.WAID API, events, localStorage)\n├── logic/\n│   ├── SlashCommand.contract.md         (/under-the-hood args, procedure, edge cases)\n│   └── LauncherScript.contract.md       (CLI signature, substitution method, exit codes)\n└── theme/\n    └── DesignTokens.contract.md         (32 colors, 23 typography, full token set)\n```\n\n**Reconciliation work I did before bringing it to you:**\n- Theme contract and UI contracts had drifted on token names (`--waid-color-fg` vs `--waid-color-text-primary`, etc.). I updated UI contracts to use the canonical theme names and added missing tokens (`--waid-content-max-width`, `--waid-toc-width`, z-index family, alias shadow tokens).\n- HtmlTemplate originally had 6 placeholders but Launcher only handled 4. I dropped `__WAID_PROJECT_NAME__` and `__WAID_SCHEMA_VERSION__` — JS now reads those from the embedded JSON instead. Single source of truth.\n\n**Open questions flagged in contracts (you decide):**\n1. `quiz.answerIndex` bounds: schema can't enforce `< choices.length`; runtime guard in JS only. **OK?**\n2. `*.csproj` glob in dotnet stack needs special handling. **Document in slash command, or add explicit `manifestFilesAreGlobs` flag?**\n3. Multi-stack monorepo `detectedStack` label: cap at 3 stacks before truncating? **Cap, or list all?**\n4. TypeScript vs JS distinction is detected by `tsconfig.json` presence — currently implicit convention in slash command. **Add explicit `variantIndicators` to schema, or leave implicit?**\n5. `unknown` stack has empty `manifestFiles` array which violates the schema's per-rule `minItems: 1`. **Drop the constraint, or use `oneOf` (named/fallback)?** I lean drop.\n\nWhat would you like to skim or change?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1658,"cache_read_input_tokens":152498,"output_tokens":884,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1658,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":884,"cache_read_input_tokens":152498,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1658,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1658},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CadEXseX9asAekBV7gxuy","type":"assistant","uuid":"3cfc869a-4328-49ff-925b-c9dc6069ee6c","timestamp":"2026-05-02T06:02:16.983Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main"}
